---
---

<style>
  .glow-wwa-blue {
    width: 1000px; height: 1000px;
    top: -450px; left: -450px;
  }
  .glow-wwa-violet {
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    bottom: -230px; right: -50px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .glow-wwa-blue {
      width: 460px; height: 460px;
      top: -207px; left: -207px;
    }
    .glow-wwa-violet {
      width: 280px; height: 280px;
      bottom: -157px; right: -23px;
    }
  }
  /* Parallax coverage only on desktop — mobile gets natural fit, no wasted GPU layer */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .whoweare-img {
      height: 115%;
      will-change: transform;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="py-28 px-6 bg-[var(--color-bg)] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute pointer-events-none glow-wwa-blue" aria-hidden="true"
       style="background: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 0%, rgba(79,110,247,0.01) 3%, rgba(79,110,247,0.02) 5%, rgba(79,110,247,0.03) 7%, rgba(79,110,247,0.06) 10%, rgba(79,110,247,0.08) 18%, rgba(79,110,247,0.10) 24%, rgba(79,110,247,0.13) 28%, rgba(79,110,247,0.15) 35%, rgba(79,110,247,0.11) 43%, rgba(79,110,247,0.06) 50%, rgba(79,110,247,0.01) 65%, rgba(79,110,247,0.0) 69%, rgba(79,110,247,0.00) 85%, transparent 100%);"></div>
  <div class="absolute pointer-events-none glow-wwa-violet" aria-hidden="true"
       style="background: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 0%, rgba(124,58,237,0.01) 3%, rgba(124,58,237,0.02) 5%, rgba(124,58,237,0.03) 7%, rgba(124,58,237,0.06) 10%, rgba(124,58,237,0.08) 18%, rgba(124,58,237,0.10) 24%, rgba(124,58,237,0.13) 28%, rgba(124,58,237,0.15) 35%, rgba(124,58,237,0.11) 43%, rgba(124,58,237,0.06) 50%, rgba(124,58,237,0.01) 65%, rgba(124,58,237,0.0) 69%, rgba(124,58,237,0.00) 85%, transparent 100%);"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10">
    <!-- Left: copy with inline stats -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-6">· Who We Are</p>
      <h2 class="font-[var(--font-heading)] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] leading-tight mb-8" data-animate-heading>
        We don't do vanity metrics. We do results.
      </h2>
      <div data-animate-body>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Serve Motions was founded on a simple belief: marketing should make businesses money. Not just generate impressions, likes, or reports that sound impressive but mean nothing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Every strategy we build is grounded in your commercial goals. We work as an extension of your team — accountable, proactive, and obsessed with measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Trusted by <span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)]"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="200"
          >200</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >+</span> clients worldwide, with a <span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)]"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="98"
          >98</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >%</span> retention rate and a <span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)]"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="5"
          >5</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold"
            style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >×</span> average ROI delivered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: professional image with clip-path reveal + Ken Burns entrance + scroll parallax -->
    <figure
      class="relative rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden m-0"
      style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; max-height: 480px;"
      data-animate-clip
    >
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=800&auto=format&q=80"
        alt="Professional team collaborating on digital strategy"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover whoweare-img"
        data-whoweare-img
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <!-- Gradient overlay: grounds image in page color at bottom, barely-perceptible blue at midpoint, clean subject area at top -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,12,20,0.7) 0%, rgba(79,110,247,0.12) 50%, transparent 100%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>
